	('Let go of my mother','Thả mẹ tôi ra','00:08:34.750','00:08:35.750','I-am-Mary-32'),
	('The man was scared to leave but was quickly caught by the security','Người đàn ông sợ hãi bỏ chạy nhưng nhanh chóng bị bảo vệ bắt giữ','00:08:36.230','00:08:39.590','I-am-Mary-32'),
	('When my father asked me, he blamed my mother again','Khi bố tôi hỏi, ông lại trách mẹ tôi','00:08:40.309','00:08:43.430','I-am-Mary-32'),
